{"word":"ἔχμα","slug":"ἔχμα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n45986\" key=\"e)/xma\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἔχμα</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ατος</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ἔχω</etym>) <sense id=\"n45986.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">that which holds</tr_>; and so, </sense> <sense n=\"I\" id=\"n45986.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">hindrance, impediment</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:21:259\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.259</biblScope> </bibl> (pl.). </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n45986.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> c. gen., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">bulwark, defence against</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐπηλυσίης</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0013.tlg004.perseus-grc1:37\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">h.Merc.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">37</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">βολάων</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:201\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.201</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n45986.3\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">holdfast, stay</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἔχματα πέτρης</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the grip</tr_> of the rock (viz. the river-bed), <bibl n=\"urn:c